总体上是满意的，但生活得又没有那么完美（房价、996等），故而从左右各派的观点中找原因。", "timestamp": 1628533141, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2242636, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Eve", "pid": 431095, "reply_to": 2242520, "tag": null, "text": "Re Angry Dave: 我的理解是小粉红的认知仅仅是舆论导向的结果，最多建立在中国短期成功的经济发展和抗疫成果上，他们的观点没有深入的思考作为根基，自然也不可能拥有坚定的认识，会随着各种突发情况而变化（例如抗疫初期，再比如当时成都“学生跳楼”事件后短期）", "timestamp": 1628534513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2242639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Eve", "pid": 431095, "reply_to": 2229620, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 👍🏻", "timestamp": 1628534544, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2243054, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Dave", "pid": 431095, "reply_to": 2242636, "tag": null, "text": "Re Angry Eve: 对对对", "timestamp": 1628553669, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2243307, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Francis", "pid": 431095, "reply_to": 2229620, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 这话我想说却组织不出语言   Carol牛啊", "timestamp": 1628559303, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2243312, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Francis", "pid": 431095, "reply_to": 2229620, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 不过对于性少数群体  我也并不支持宣传   这个群体存在确实也合理  但是我只能不诋毁，不支持", "timestamp": 1628559604, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 56, "pid": 431095, "reply": 41, "tag": null, "text": "进入树洞以来，你见过跟自己以前的认知相差最大的观点是啥？", "timestamp": 1628399902, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1628559603, "url": "", "vote": {}}}